<paragraph pageNumber="455">Figure Unique holotype, major. PERU: Cuzco Amazonico, 15 km northeast of Puerto Maldonado, Madre de Dios (Stefan Cover and John E. Tobin). Minor unknown. Scale bar = 1 mm.</paragraph>
